game.name: Frozen Winter Dress Up
game.description:
Winter has just come and the two lovely Disney princesses Anna and Elsa have found themselves surrounded by a big trouble! They have noticed that snow and ice are everywhere in their castle. The winter is at its peak in Arendelle and your two princesses have not decided yet what to put on to protect themselves against the cold waves. Would you love to help them out right away? Join Elsa And Anna Winter Dress Up game and be prepared to help them pick up the warm outfits before going out!
The best part is that their wardrobe is full of fashionable yet warm outfits to wear. All you need to do is browse their wider outfit and accessory options to dress them up perfectly in this brand new dressing game for girls. Anna likes to put on the comfortable dresses, so give your girl a nice oversized red knitted sweater-dress and match it with a pair of black color ankle boots with fur. Do not forget to complete her look with a white hat with a flower on the side, a pair of suitable gloves and green color stocking. 
Elsa usually wears the proper warm dresses, so you can dress her up with a purple color blouse, and combine it with a short denim skirt and blue color jacket. Complete her look with a very fluffy hat, a pair of purple gloves and a pair of black boots with hells in this html5 princess dress up game! Keep mixing and matching other items until you realize that you have created the perfect dresses for both of them! Enjoy more girls dress up simulation games that are free to play online, no download required on atmegame.com!
